{"tid":690381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(二戰JJ)Post Scriptum - The Bloody Seventh","createTime":"2018-06-04T22:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T09:20:21.000Z","uid":59743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd482d690556209a850ca05caf1db6a8e99dc5c","tid":690381,"uid":59743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://postscriptumgame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Halftrack_Branded_v011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FHalftrack_Branded_v011.jpg&h=e6388b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說上星期睇完Battlefield 5 個trailer,見到女人士兵走黎走去,裝左機械手腳既士兵上2戰戰埸,戰機機師炒機轉身返落地,v2火箭射落黎近距離轟炸之後咩事都無.......忍唔住係度開返個post<br />\n<br />\n鐘意玩2戰game既你,黎緊就出一隻叫Post Scriptum - The Bloody Seventh 既遊戲<br />\n<br />\n故事係講2戰 美軍同英軍空降部隊(British Airborne Division, British XXX Corps)打德軍(Wehrmacht or the Waffen SS)<br />\n<br />\n呢隻game既特點和定位:<br />\n-50vs50,<br />\n-真實2戰模擬器,差唔多一槍死(類似red orchestra 2, Squad)<br />\n-要同小團隊有非常好既合作,一齊傾戰略,搶有利位置搶資訊,每個小團隊有唔同既2戰士兵職業(medic,machine gunner, masksman, anti-tank,rifleman,engineer,tank commander, tank crew, driver,gunner,hull gunner,etc) <br />\n-5張超大地圖 (&gt;140 KM)<br />\n-50種真實載具(雪曼,虎式,etc)<br />\n-40種真實槍械<br />\n-指揮官可以起營地(叫轟炸機)<br />\n-細緻坦克設計<br />\n-盟軍可以玩跳傘<br />\n<br />\n遊戲設計師係Squad MOD TEAM,由2016年3月開始設計<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴打自己上官網睇: <a href=\"http://postscriptumgame.com/the-game/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fthe-game%2F&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=11ccb8f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://postscriptumgame.com/the-game/</a><br />\n<br />\ntrailer: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yFKNSu_aI5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyFKNSu_aI5I&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=607868a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yFKNSu_aI5I</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=ClhAxd_XR-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D3%26v%3DClhAxd_XR-8&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=375d3852\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=ClhAxd_XR-8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://postscriptumgame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/C47_Branded_v011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpostscriptumgame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2FC47_Branded_v011.jpg&h=0ede27c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99d7084e23a708ea9ca4ba8efb303fcdc9791634","tid":690381,"uid":142604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲驚 亞洲冇人玩架啦<br />\n除左手機驚 fornite pubg仲識啲咩<br />\nSteam幾萬人玩既 亞洲都唔知有冇一千人<br />\n更何況呢類hardcore fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a042f604d89439b7139104717b3de8a8ce3972f6","tid":690381,"uid":45286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d7084e23a708ea9ca4ba8efb303fcdc9791634","tid":690381,"uid":142604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲驚 亞洲冇人玩架啦<br />\n除左手機驚 fornite pubg仲識啲咩<br />\nSteam幾萬人玩既 亞洲都唔知有冇一千人<br />\n更何況呢類hardcore fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:00:55.000Z","msg":"wt wot都係因為有架仔野先多啲亞洲人玩<br />\n呢隻歐洲戰場為主應該無乜人理㗎啦<br />\n利申:放左係wishlist等有錢/特價"},{"pid":"4fdcebbb468a3d947bce55a747ec6e01886c9035","tid":690381,"uid":142604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a042f604d89439b7139104717b3de8a8ce3972f6","tid":690381,"uid":45286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d7084e23a708ea9ca4ba8efb303fcdc9791634","tid":690381,"uid":142604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:56:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲驚 亞洲冇人玩架啦<br />\n除左手機驚 fornite pubg仲識啲咩<br />\nSte